{"id": 61075, "date": "2025-10-08T04:00:54", "date_gmt": "2025-10-08T11:00:54", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61075"}, "modified": "2026-06-14T06:24:44", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-14T13:24:44", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-october-8-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/08/kingdom-of-days-october-8-2/", "title": {"rendered": "October 8"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1965:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles play what is believed to be their first publicly advertised gig at the I.B. Club in Howell, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4740\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1965-1008/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1965-1008.jpg?fit=476%2C534&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"476,534\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1965-1008\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1965-1008.jpg?fit=476%2C534&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4740 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1965-1008.jpg?resize=476%2C534&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"476\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1965-1008.jpg?w=476&amp;ssl=1 476w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1965-1008.jpg?resize=267%2C300&amp;ssl=1 267w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 476px) 100vw, 476px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1971:</strong> The Bruce Springsteen Band headlines at The Ledge at Rutgers University.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong><em>Born to Run</em> is certified gold by the Recording Industry Association of America.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_nZs0gvllzGn7y9-5OuorN7W37HPrPGrn8\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band record &#8220;Party Lights&#8221; at The Power Station in New York City. It will remain unreleased\u00a0 for more than 35 years.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/S2WWQAvS_6I?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Fresh off the fifteen-month Born in the U.S.A. Tour, Nils appears on <em>Late Night with David Letterman.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Sm-860N8T1w?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1987:\u00a0</strong>Bruce films the video for &#8220;Brilliant Disguise&#8221; at Fort Hancock in Sandy Hook, New Jersey, singing the vocal live over the album&#8217;s instrumental track for a remarkable 24 takes. Meiert Avis directs the shoot and the video. We are fortunate to have his lengthy and fascinating recollection of the events.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/idnJnjV_8rg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4747\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1987-1008/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1987-1008.jpg?fit=1200%2C822&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1200,822\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1987-1008\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1987-1008.jpg?fit=758%2C519&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4747 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1987-1008-300x206.jpg?resize=744%2C510\" alt=\"\" width=\"744\" height=\"510\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1987-1008.jpg?resize=300%2C206&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1987-1008.jpg?resize=768%2C526&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1987-1008.jpg?resize=1024%2C701&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1987-1008.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" /></p>\n<p>That evening, Bruce joins Little Steven and the Disciples of Soul at The Ritz in New York City, where they perform &#8220;Native American&#8221; and &#8220;Sun City.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WkJkooAjDrg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>A scheduled show at Mountain View&#8217;s Shoreline Amphitheater is postponed until later in the month after Bruce takes ill.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29946\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1992-10-08-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1992-10-08.jpg?fit=398%2C1851&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"398,1851\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1601240069&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1992-10-08\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1992-10-08.jpg?fit=220%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29946 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1992-10-08.jpg?resize=398%2C1851&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"398\" height=\"1851\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1992-10-08.jpg?w=398&amp;ssl=1 398w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1992-10-08.jpg?resize=220%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 220w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1992-10-08.jpg?resize=330%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 330w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 398px) 100vw, 398px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1998:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and Mike Appel testify in the Royal Courts of Justice in London to prevent the unauthorized publication of some of Bruce&#8217;s early recorded but unreleased songs.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21702\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1998-10-08a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?fit=2432%2C739&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2432,739\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1601240288&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1998-10-08a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?fit=758%2C230&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21702 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?resize=758%2C230&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"230\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?w=2432&amp;ssl=1 2432w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?resize=300%2C91&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?resize=1024%2C311&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?resize=768%2C233&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?resize=1536%2C467&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?resize=2048%2C622&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08a.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21703\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1998-10-08b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?fit=1617%2C1647&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1617,1647\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1601240421&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1998-10-08b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?fit=758%2C772&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21703 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?resize=758%2C772&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"772\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?w=1617&amp;ssl=1 1617w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?resize=295%2C300&amp;ssl=1 295w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?resize=1005%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1005w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?resize=768%2C782&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?resize=1508%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1508w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1998-10-08b.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2004:\u00a0</strong>The Vote for Change Tour stops in Orlando, where Tracy Chapman joins Bruce on stage for &#8220;My Hometown&#8221; and Bruce guests with R.E.M. on &#8220;Permanent Vacation.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/imXUy4RyuNw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;start=3&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZfxMHXJZdnU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kTduOCEP8Es?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Okem2CboVhM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2006:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the Sessions Band play a show at Palamaggio in Caserta, Italy.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oh4pznAPHkg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QY14JREQrUM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mWKhbNVX9L0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>At Night Four of five at Giants Stadium on the Working on a Dream Tour, Bruce and the E Street Band perform the entire\u00a0<em>Born to Run\u00a0</em>album, during which Jake Clemons makes an early E Street appearance with Ed Manion and Curt Ramm on &#8220;Tenth Avenue Freeze-Out.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wSNy8KR9dZc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0khn6CH9JVA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nUQIhK5hrIM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/riZd29bvuls?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2011:\u00a0</strong>Ben Stiller reprises his impeccable Bruce Springsteen impression when he guest-hosts\u00a0<em>Saturday Night Live\u00a0</em>and pitches a box set that in all honesty many fans would probably buy. (I know I would.)</p>\n<div id=\"v-osGXxOxb-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/osGXxOxb?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce shoots the video for &#8220;Brilliant Disguise,&#8221; Nils drops by David Letterman&#8217;s show, Jake makes an early E Street Band appearance back in 2009, and Ben Stiller resurrects his Bruce impression on SNL. More highlights inside.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 4768, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "foo